### Change 2: Fix page 2 CSS — don't force min-height on continuation pages

**FILE**: [index.css](file:///c:/Users/pc/Desktop/seve/src/index.css)

**ADD** inside the `@media screen` block (after line 796, before the closing `}`):

```css
  /* Page 2+ should shrink to fit content, not force full A4 height */
  .resume-page-continuation {
    min-height: auto !important;
  }
```

This ensures page 2 doesn't show massive white space when it only has a few sections.

